wn to cause thrombosis should be used with caution in multiple myeloma patients receiving thalidomide with standard chemotherapeutic agents and/or steroids.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/170794/', '', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, More', '', 1767369485);
