wn to cause thrombosis should be used with caution in multiple myeloma patients receiving thalidomide with standard chemotherapeutic agents and/or steroids.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/170825/', '', 'Darolutamide, Aminoglutethimide, Fulvestrant', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, More', 1767369485);
